IoTSharp.CoAP.NET
=================

This project is the .NET 10 library project for the IoTSharp-maintained
CoAP.NET fork. The package keeps both client and server APIs, blockwise
transfer, observe support, UDP transport, and PSK DTLS transport.

Use the repository-level README.md for current quick-start, logging, DTLS, and
NuGet packaging instructions.
